qid=20090111214056AAkaXBc_answer_1	1	qid=20090111214056AAkaXBc	2009-01-12 23:32:14 +0000	best_answer	 Yes ... this is a good place to stay for the weekend . You can do things such as hang out at the beach , shop , lots of restaurants , kayak , snorkel , glass bottom boat ride , miniature golf , hiking , take a tram tour of the island , rent a golf cart , see a movie , go to the botanical gardens , etc. . I would not suggest staying for more than 2-3 days as the town is very small and you may run out of things to do after that time .
