qid=20090111214056AAkaXBc_answer_7	2	qid=20090111214056AAkaXBc	2009-01-12 22:10:28 +0000	answer	 It 's a very nice place for a SHORT TIME get away . It can be crowded on weekends so your better bargain will be during the week . The island is small and there are lots of things to see , and do , but by the end of the second day you 've seen it all . Most of the activities revolve around the ENTITY_City_of_Avalon . Automobiles are rare on the island so rent golf carts , or bicycles to get around , however if that stretches your budget most things are within a short walk . Inquire about the inland things like horse back riding , etc. . It will be a good educational experience for your daughter . Include ENTITY_Catalina_Island as a part of a vacation in the greater ENTITY_Los_Angeles area .
